<p> 2024 年怀特岛音乐节最后一天的演出包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/simple-minds">Simple Minds</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nothing-but-thieves">Nothing But Thieves</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beverly-knight">Beverly Knight</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mcfly">McFly</a> 。</p><p>其他演出阵容包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cian-ducrot">Cian Ducrot</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caity-baser">Caity Baser</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/s-club">S Club、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-meighan">Tom Meighan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/scouting-for-girls">Scouting For Girls</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zara-larsson">Zara Larsson</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-darkness">The Darkness</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/toyah-willcox">Toyah</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-fripp">Robert Fripp</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-mary-wallopers">The Mary Wallopers</a>等。</p><p>查看下面海报中的当前阵容，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fisle-of-wight-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F28397" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处购买门票</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3582600" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3582600" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3582600" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/IOW-poster@2000x2000.jpg" alt="怀特岛 2024 年海报" width="2000" height="2076" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/IOW-poster@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/IOW-poster@2000x2000-400x415.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/IOW-poster@2000x2000-800x830.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/IOW-poster@2000x2000-696x722.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/IOW-poster@2000x2000-1392x1445.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/IOW-poster@2000x2000-1068x1109.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3582600" class="wp-caption-text">怀特岛 2024 年海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>早在 11 月，绿日乐队就已确认即将在周日（6 月 23 日）举行的头条新闻<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-pet-shop-boys-and-the-prodigy-to-headline-isle-of-wight-festival-2024-lineup-buy-tickets-3528939">将是他们 2024 年唯一的英国节日表演</a>。</p><p>音乐节发起人约翰·吉丁斯 (John Giddings) 在宣布初步阵容时表示：“我们很高兴今天宣布 2024 年的头条人物，并继续为明年的音乐节展示一系列真正令人兴奋的人才。</p><p> “从全球知名的先锋艺术家，到排行榜上的顶尖人才和后起之秀，我们迫不及待地欢迎大家明年来到岛上。粉丝们请继续关注更多消息！”</p><p> 2023 年怀特岛音乐节举办了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-george-ezra-the-chemical-brothers-and-robbie-williams-to-headline-isle-of-wight-festival-2023-3339295">Pulp、The Chemical Brothers、Robbie Williams 和 George Ezra 的精彩表演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/johnny-marr-suede-the-pretenders-among-50-new-names-for-isle-of-wight-2024-line-up-3582590">Johnny Marr、Suede、The Pretenders 等 50 个怀特岛 2024 年阵容的新名字</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
